    "description": "<p>You attempt to Charm a creature within range. Choose a&nbsp;Non-Hostile creature that can see and hear you.</p>\n<p>Make a <strong>Spell </strong><strong>Check </strong>contested by the target&rsquo;s <strong>Charisma Save</strong>.</p>\n<p><strong>Success:</strong> You&nbsp;have ADV on all <strong>Charisma Checks </strong>made against this creature.&nbsp;When the spell effect ends or you fail the check the creature<br>realizes that you used magic to influence its mood and may&nbsp;become hostile towards you.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Mana Point Enhancements</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Hostile Charm: (1 MP)</strong> Cast this on any creature.</li>\n<li><strong>Clear Suspicion: (2 MP)</strong> Target will no longer&nbsp;realize that magic has been cast on them.</li>\n<li><strong>More Friends: (2 MP)</strong> Add an additional target to the effect of this spell and increase the range by 10 Spaces.</li>\n</ul>",
